name: Global X USD Cash Maximizer Corporate Class ETF
longDescription: Horizons HSUV.U invests substantially all of its assets in high interest U.S. dollar deposit accounts with one or more Canadian chartered banks. Horizons HSUV.U can also invest in high-quality, short-term (one year or less) debt securities, including U.S. dollar denominated treasury bills and promissory notes issued or guaranteed by the United States federal government or the Government of Canada, or their respective agencies, and U.S. dollar denominated bankers acceptances. HSUV.U seeks to generate modest capital growth.
